<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4269.1.3>
    bibo:endPage "100" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "61" ;
    bibo:volume "4269" ;
    dc:creator "Laamiri, Sayef" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Myxosporea (Cnidaria: Myxozoa) infecting the saddled seabream Oblada melanura (L. 1758) (Teleostei: Sparidae) and the painted comber Serranus scriba (L. 1758) (Teleostei: Serranidae) in Tunisia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.581307> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.581307>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Photomicrographs of Ceratomyxa sp. 1 from the gall bladder of Serranus scriba. (A – F) Variable forms of fresh mature spores in sutural view presenting the pyriform polar capsules (pc), the straight suture line (sl), the sporoplasmic nuclei (sn), the capsulogenic nucleus (cn) and the unequal valves. Scale bar = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/581307/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

